How to apply




Things you should know before applying
In line with anti-money laundering regulations, we need to have a record of your personal identification (ID) before we can open an investment for you.
To help us process your application as quickly as possible, please call us to confirm if we have a record of your ID. If not, we may ask you to take one of the following forms of ID to your nearest branch: 

Current passport
Current full UK driving licence
National ID Card
Armed Forces Card


